Focusing on change projects in Andalucia


=Description=

"Guadal: Journey to a Post Crisis Economy is an act of solidarity and relationship building. It is an action research project and a documentary film. Beginning in late June, we’ll travel through communities in Andalusia, visiting citizen-led projects that are building new solutions and new models of economic participation, cooperation, solidarity and innovation. As we go, we’ll be building connections between our projects and our community in Totnes, with the projects and communities there.  We want to learn from their experience and bring back new knowledge, just as we wish to share the lessons. Everyone is invited to share in this journey. Finally, we will collect our stories into a full-length documentary, sharing the successes and challenges with the wider world."
(http://guadal.org/video/)


